ORDER

In the Matter of EDWIN B. BORISON, an attorney at law. May 12, 1987.

This matter having been duly considered by the Court, it is OEDEEED that EDWIN E. BOEISON, of OKLAHOMA CITY, OKLAHOMA, who was admitted to the bar of this State in 1965, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
